overview.en: Uni-Nutrition Certificate will introduce a general currency, called UITC (union raising token chain) into the platform ecosystem. UITC will be used as a value pass, contract incentive and payment tool in all application scenarios to meet all transaction requirements.
overview.zh: 联养通证将在平台生态系统中引入一种通用货币，称为 UITC (union raising token chain)。UITC 将用作所有应用场景中的价 值通证、合约奖励及支付手段，满足所有交易需求.
